org.araneaframework.uilib.support
Class FileInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.araneaframework.uilib.support.FileInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class FileInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable

This file represents a file info received from a FileUploadControl. Besides common file attributes (name, original name, size and type) this class also provides a readFileContent() method, which allows to read the file content into memory as a byte[]

Author:
Jevgeni Kabanov (ekabanov@araneaframework.org)
